          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                ".0.4 MBq of Cs-137 was used as a sample contained in",
                " a 0.003 liters of Ca-Cl solution which was then",
                " evaporated to dryness and deposited at the bottom",
                " of the bottle as a thin disk 7 mm diam. and less than",
                " 0.5 mm thick. Accurate number of Cs-137 atoms was",
                " determined relative to Cs-138 product atoms about",
                " 30 min after irradiation",
                ".Monitor samples were 0.475% Co/Al and 0.061% Au/Al",
                " alloys wires 0.76 and 0.51 mm diameter, 3 mm long",
                " sticked on the outside of the sample bottle."
              ]
            }
          ],
